This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a method for automating the architecture design of generative models using neural architecture search. It is also likely to belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the proposed method is specifically tailored for generative models in image generation tasks. Additionally, it may belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks and optimization algorithms. Finally, it may belong to cs.GR (Graphics) as it focuses on generative models for image generation.
